<title>CSS Test: Test declaring a variable whose value is "unset" where there is a variable to inherit from.</title><title>CSS Test: Test declaring a variable whose value is "unset" where there is a variable to inherit from.</title><title>CSS Test: Test declaring a variable whose value is "unset" where there is a variable to inherit from.</title><link rel="match" title="Cameron McCormack"><title>CSS Test: Test declaring a variable whose value is "unset" where there is a variable to inherit from.</title><style>
body {
  --a: green;
  color: crimson;
}
p {
  color: orange;
  --a: unset;
  color: var(--a);
}
</style>
